description: Lovingly restored and maintained single family just one block from West Broadway. This home has been completely renovated to feature an amazing first floor that creates a magnificent entertaining space. The kitchen was remodeled with granite counters, stainless steel appliances and opens to the dining area which features a built in china cabinet. The dining area flows seamlessly into the living room complete with gas fireplace for those winter nights. On the second floor you'll find two bedrooms, one with a Murphy bed which is great for guests. There is also an office on this floor and the full bathroom was also renovated. Walk upstairs to your private primary suite with ensuite bathroom, a walk in closet and another bonus room waiting for your vision. The basement has also been completely redone to make a perfect au pair/in law suite with a full bathroom and Murphy bed. Also the perfect outdoor space for back yard bbqs!  And the location cannot be beat! This home is one of a kind!
